4
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:38,000
 The sort of most frustrating thing is the startup failure.

5
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:44,000
 And this is where you see the something went wrong when you navigate to your application on Python anywhere.

6
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:51,000
 But this really said is we're trying to get your application started, and we have failed in doing that.

7
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:52,000
