8
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:55,000
 We can't show your application because it doesn't run.

9
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:01,000
 Your application is so broken that Python anywhere can't even start it.

10
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:09,000
 So you can start an application, and if you start it, you can still have bugs or problems in your application.

11
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:12,000
 And those are these yellow screens, the traceback.

12
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:15,000
