 If you look at the previous one, it didn't load.

221
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:14,000
 I just changed one thing here.

222
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:17,000
 And it made it all the way to my application before it blew up.

223
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:22,000
 Now it's running the application where I have to do a request.

224
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:25,000
 Blowing up with the something went wrong.

225
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:28,000
 Before you even send it a request, it's already broken.

226
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:31,000
 So I'm going to just fix this.

227
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:37,000
 So you'll notice that when I hit the save button, all the little upside down arrows.

228
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:39,000
 The little yellow triangles go away.

229
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,000
 So that's a good sign.

230
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,000
 Not a guarantee.

231
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:45,000
 But it's trying to help you avoid mistakes.

232
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,000
 Sometimes you're cutting and pasting things in here.

233
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:50,000
 You've cut and pasted something twice.

234
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:58,000
 Et cetera, et cetera, et cetera.

235
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:00,000
 And hit reload on this.

236
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:02,000
 And there it works.

237
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:06,000
 That basically is the kinds of things when you see a traceback.

238
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:09,000
 There are all kinds of things that can go wrong with a traceback.

239
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,000
 You can have a missing template file.

240
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:14,000
 You can have a syntax error in a template file.

241
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:17,000
 You can have an include that wasn't included the right way.

242
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:20,000
 Your database migrations may not have been.

243
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:26,000
 And you just kind of got to read all this stuff at the top and get used to it.

244
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:37,000
 And so I hope that this has been helpful and helps you to be able to debug some of your applications.

245
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,000
 Cheers.

